snippet.textDisplay: I'm so done with the comments that are just "Why doesn't Tae talk or smile?!" Maybe he just doesn't feel like it. Or he could be depressed, in which case it's not helpful to say things like "Omg are you okayyyy you look so down please be happy and smile~~" Like, if the guy feels down let him feel down, don't pressure him to cover it up with a smile.
